Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你迷路了对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  迷路了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  我来把你送回家里的说
